p.k: Unikitty discovers Puppycorn's only other friend is a boring old rock. / When Hawkodile develops a secret crush on Dr. Fox, he finds himself crushing down in size! Being too embarrassed to tell her about it, Unikitty & the gang become his love gurus! / After a workplace injury, Richard is unable to do his servant work. / Puppycorn finally realizes he’s a prince & wants to oversee the kingdom! Despite their friends’ concerns, Unikitty makes him ruler but the power is too much for him to handle.
